  "designNotes": "Both hands are needed to lift the keystone, so pre-clear the warden and drifters and pre-set the rotators first; rotator1=1 bridges gap A but drops the corridor-B portcullis, so relay the keystone: carry across gap A, set it down, flip rotator1=2 to open corridor B, then carry over rotator2's gap-B bridge onto the mass-3 keystone plate.",
  "intro": "The keystone needs both hands \u2014 so clear the road and set the spans before you lift, for you cannot fight nor turn a wheel while you carry.",
